mode	󰉋  /files · Files	mode.files	__mode__	Folders, projects and recent files.	system-file-manager
mode	󰒓  /settings · Settings	mode.settings	__mode__	System controls and SevenOS settings.	preferences-system
mode	󰐊  /system · System Actions	mode.system	__mode__	SevenOS actions, profiles, security and runtime commands.	system-run
mode	󰖟  /web · Web & Intelligence	mode.web	__mode__	Calculations, conversions, definitions, web, mail, contacts and calendar.	web-browser
intent	󰚩  Ask · Why is my system slow?	ai.system.slow	seven insights	Analyze SevenOS readiness, services and bottlenecks.	system-search
intent	󰁹  Ask · Optimize battery	ai.battery	seven scheduler plan	Show power-aware scheduler recommendations.	battery
intent	󰒃  Ask · Prepare Cyber workspace	ai.cyber	seven shield mode	Open CyberSpace context and actions.	security-high
intent	󰅩  Ask · Prepare Dev workspace	ai.forge	seven profile activate forge	Switch to Forge development context.	applications-development
intent	󰏗  Ask · Prepare Studio workspace	ai.studio	seven profile activate studio	Switch to Studio creative context.	applications-graphics
calc	󰃬  Calculator · Type an expression	calc.help	__calc__	Try: 42*7, (128/4)+9, 15% of 240	accessories-calculator
